罗森塔尔夫人？
Frau Rosenthal?

29
00:07:00,780 --> 00:07:03,210
有我丈夫的信吗
Anything from my husband?

30
00:07:13,820 --> 00:07:14,920
谢谢你 爱娃
Thank you, Eva

31
00:07:14,930 --> 00:07:16,390
