You have milk and eggs

41
00:09:35,700 --> 00:09:38,130
- 还需要多少黄油？ - 我…
- Now how much butter do you need?  - I.

42
00:09:39,570 --> 00:09:40,640
拜托
Oh, come on!

43
00:09:40,640 --> 00:09:41,970
- 过来  - 快点
- Come along  - Hurry up

44
00:09:49,350 --> 00:09:52,580
昆格尔夫人 我送你回家
Frau Quangel? I'll take you home

45
