- 奥托  - 我在写字
- Otto?  - I'm writing

129
00:19:00,430 --> 00:19:01,860
写给谁
To who?

130
00:19:02,630 --> 00:19:04,300
我不知道
I don't know

131
00:19:06,500 --> 00:19:08,500
我在写卡片
I'm writing cards

132
00:19:09,540 --> 00:19:11,540
讲述真相的卡片
Cards that tell the truth

133
00:19:16,680 --> 00:19:18,750
人们会看到这些卡片
People will read these cards

134
00:19:21,950 --> 00:19:24,020
会相互传阅
They will pass them on

135
00:19:30,130 --> 00:19:31,790
卡片？
Cards?

136
00:19:33,160 --> 00:19:34,730
你在写卡片？
You're scribbling cards?

137
00:19:34,730 --> 00:19:36,830
这有什么用处
What is that supposed to do?

138
