如果她喊叫怎么办
What if she screams?

145
00:20:38,830 --> 00:20:40,730
她不会喊叫的
She won't scream

146
00:20:41,900 --> 00:20:44,100
我的笨老婆还给她送饭
My stupid wife takes food to her

147
00:20:44,100 --> 00:20:45,630
那个老犹太人
The old Jew

148
00:20:47,040 --> 00:20:50,840
她的店被人烧了之后 她把东西都拉到这里来了
She hauled all her stuff up here after they burned her shop

149
00:20:53,310 --> 00:20:54,680
她在躲藏
She's hiding

150
00:21:14,530 --> 00:21:15,860
安静
Calm down

151
00:21:23,770 --> 00:21:25,110
爸爸 楼上
Papa, upstairs

152
00:21:25,110 --> 00:21:26,940
我们走 快
Let's go. Quickly

153
00:21:39,020 --> 00:21:40,860
你来这里干什么
What are you doing here?

154
00:21:42,120 --> 00:21:46,160
巴克豪森 你来这房子干什么
Barkhausen, what are you doing in this apartment?

155
00:21:46,160 --> 00:21:48,100
帕西卡先生
Herr Persicke.

156
00:21:48,100 --> 00:21:50,600
邻居 我们可以分享
Neighbor, we can share

157
00:21:57,370 --> 00:21:59,370
是罗森塔尔夫人
It's Frau Rosenthal

158
00:22:14,820 --> 00:22:17,390
- 拜托 这不是我的错  - 出去
- Please, it's not my fault  - Out

159
00:22:19,590 --> 00:22:21,260
找钱
Look for the money

160
00:22:29,440 --> 00:22:31,740
我很抱歉
I'm sorry

161
00:22:31,740 --> 00:22:33,740
没必要抱歉
There's no need to be

162
00:22:34,880 --> 00:22:37,340
你可以住在我们这里
You can stay with us

163
00:22:37,350 --> 00:22:40,210
这对你太危险了
This is too dangerous for you

164
00:23:37,740 --> 00:23:40,610
- 嘘  - 弗洛姆法官
- Ssh.  - Judge Fromm?

165
00:23:40,610 --> 00:23:43,740
跟我来夫人 快
Come with me, madame Quickly

166
00:23:43,750 --> 00:23:45,280
他们还会来的
They'll be back

167
00:23:50,190 --> 00:23:52,350
嘘 安静 进去
Ssh, be quiet. Come in

168
00:24:11,010 --> 00:24:13,170
我已故女儿的房间
My deceased daughter's room

169
00:24:13,180 --> 00:24:15,440
没人会来这里找你
No one will look for you here

170
00:24:15,440 --> 00:24:17,610
尽量适应一下这里
Try to get used to it

171
00:24:17,610 --> 00:24:19,350
去睡觉到明早
Go to sleep and tomorrow morning

172
00:24:19,350 --> 00:24:21,420
你要一切按我说的做
you will listen exactly to what I say

173
00:24:21,420 --> 00:24:22,850
明天
Tomorrow

174
00:24:22,850 --> 00:24:24,950
晚安 罗森塔尔夫人
Goodnight, Frau Rosenthal

175
00:25:04,990 --> 00:25:06,990
她回她的家了吗
Is she back in her apartment?

176
00:25:30,190 --> 00:25:32,250
- 不行  - 我跟你一起去
- No  - I'm coming with you

177
00:25:32,250 --> 00:25:34,360
你休想拦住我
You can't stop me

178
00:25:34,360 --> 00:25:35,690
你休想拦住我
You can't stop me

179
00:25:35,690 --> 00:25:37,730
他们会绞死你的 他们也会绞死女人
They'll hang you They hang women, too

180
00:25:37,730 --> 00:25:39,360
他们当然会
Of course they do

181
00:25:45,430 --> 00:25:48,240
你只去办公楼前
You only go up to the building

182
00:25:48,240 --> 00:25:50,500
我进去放置卡片
I go inside. I place the card

183
00:26:47,730 --> 00:26:49,430
我很快回来
I'll be right back

184
00:28:00,500 --> 00:28:02,300
我等会就接待你
I'll be with you in a minute

185
00:28:02,300 --> 00:28:03,770
这里来先生
This way, sir

186
00:28:04,840 --> 00:28:06,510
八十芬尼
80 pfennig, please

187
00:29:05,030 --> 00:29:07,730
- 一杯杜松子酒  - 我要一杯咖啡
- A schnapps  - Coffee for me

188
00:29:07,740 --> 00:29:09,840
不了 我也要一杯杜松子酒
No, I'll have a schnapps, too

189
00:29:15,910 --> 00:29:17,580
那么我们开始了
So, we begin

190
00:29:23,450 --> 00:29:25,450
从今以后我们就孤军作战了
From now on we are alone

191
00:29:34,460 --> 00:29:36,430
在一段时间内
You will not leave this room

192
00:29:36,430 --> 00:29:38,000
你不能离开这房间
for a certain period of time

193
00:29:38,000 --> 00:29:41,440
可能要很长时间 你是我的客人
Possibly a long time, you are my guest

194
00:29:41,440 --> 00:29:43,570
但相信我
But believe me

195
00:29:43,570 --> 00:29:46,140
只要你一走出这个门
the moment you step out of that door

196
00:29:46,140 --> 00:29:48,610
我就不认识你了
I will no longer know you

197
