洛林大街分局打来的电话
Incoming call from the Lothringer street section

572
01:04:24,480 --> 01:04:27,790
说是逮捕了淘气鬼一案的嫌疑犯
Reported arrest of suspect in the hobgoblin case

573
01:04:27,790 --> 01:04:29,220
好的 我为你接通
Yes, I'll put you through

574
01:04:52,210 --> 01:04:53,650
安娜
Anna

575
01:04:53,650 --> 01:04:55,210
你好 沃尔特
Oh, hello, Walter

576
01:04:55,220 --> 01:04:58,380
- 他私奔了吗 可怜的姑娘  - 不是
- Did he run away? Poor girl  - No

577
01:04:58,390 --> 01:05:00,720
我只是把他的饭盒带来 他又忘在家了
I just brought him his lunch box. He left it again

578
01:05:00,720 --> 01:05:03,890
我还以为他病了 他没来上班
Oh, I thought he was ill He isn't here

579
01:05:32,990 --> 01:05:36,390
安娜 你好吗 你真好看
Anna, how are you doing? You look great

580
01:05:36,390 --> 01:05:38,290
我快要结婚了
I'm getting married soon!

581
01:05:48,300 --> 01:05:51,270
- 绞死他太便宜他了  - 叛徒
- Hanging's too good for you!  - Traitor!

582
01:05:55,140 --> 01:05:58,010
你是个叛徒 你是人民的敌人
You're a traitor! You're an enemy to the people!

583
01:05:58,010 --> 01:05:59,610
- 噢  - 你在这儿干什么
- Oh!  - What are you doing here?

584
01:05:59,610 --> 01:06:02,110
等等 我们说过我们一起干的
Oh, wait We said we'd do this together

585
01:06:05,150 --> 01:06:07,190
- 你怎么没去工作  - 现在不方便
- Why didn't you go to work?  - Not now

586
01:06:11,420 --> 01:06:12,590
叛徒
Traitor!

587
01:06:21,470 --> 01:06:23,540
你知道我今天是什么心情吗
Do you know what my day was like?

588
01:06:26,170 --> 01:06:27,870
你没考虑过吧
No. You don't think of that, do you?

589
01:06:27,870 --> 01:06:29,140
发现你不在工厂
Finding you're not at work

590
01:06:29,140 --> 01:06:30,580
然后想到你还在大楼里面
and then thinking you're still inside that building

591
01:06:30,580 --> 01:06:31,910
你知道我是什么心情吗
You know what that's like for me?

592
01:06:31,910 --> 01:06:33,450
怎么了奥托 你想被抓住吗
What is it, Otto? You want to get caught?

593
01:06:33,450 --> 01:06:35,010
是这样吗
Is that what it is?

594
01:06:43,490 --> 01:06:45,990
- 没出什么事  - 没出什么事？
- Nothing happened  - Nothing happened?

595
01:06:45,990 --> 01:06:48,560
你看到他们逮捕了谁吗
Did you see who they arrested?

596
01:06:48,560 --> 01:06:50,430
一个流氓 可能是偷了东西
A bum He probably stole something

597
01:06:50,430 --> 01:06:51,630
跟我们没关系
It has nothing to do with us

598
01:06:51,630 --> 01:06:55,670
他是我们的女邮递员的丈夫
That's the husband of our postmistress

599
01:06:55,670 --> 01:06:58,070
你怎么觉得跟我们没关系
What makes you think it has nothing to do with us?

600
01:06:58,070 --> 01:06:59,400
他们离婚了
They're divorced

601
01:07:00,940 --> 01:07:03,410
这不能说明什么 真是的
That doesn't mean anything, damn it!

602
01:07:04,480 --> 01:07:07,080
我很担心你
I was so afraid for you

603
01:07:07,080 --> 01:07:10,550
如果这是个征兆是个警告呢
What if it's a, a sign, if it's a warning?

604
01:07:10,550 --> 01:07:11,750
这不是
It isn't

605
01:07:14,720 --> 01:07:16,020
镇定
Stay calm

606
01:07:22,930 --> 01:07:25,030
记得汉斯死的时候
Remember, when Hans died.

607
01:07:26,300 --> 01:07:28,400
你说过你活着没什么价值吗
You said your life wasn't worth a thing?

608
01:07:31,200 --> 01:07:33,470
你说的对
You were right

609
01:07:33,470 --> 01:07:35,440
所以我们能解脱
That's why we can be free

610
01:07:35,440 --> 01:07:37,310
所以我们能无所畏惧
why we don't have to be afraid

611
01:07:37,310 --> 01:07:39,480
但你活着
But your life

612
01:07:39,480 --> 01:07:41,680
奥托 你活着 对我来说有价值
Otto, your life means something to me now

613
01:07:41,680 --> 01:07:44,080
对我
means, means.

614
01:07:45,120 --> 01:07:46,720
对我来说 意味着一切
Everything to me now

615
01:07:50,690 --> 01:07:52,490
我们说过我们一起干的
We said we'd do this together

616
01:07:52,490 --> 01:07:54,360
哦
Oh.

617
01:07:54,360 --> 01:07:57,460
- 我们不会罢手  - 你不怕吗
- We won't stop  - Aren't you afraid?

618
01:08:01,530 --> 01:08:03,570
今天我又停下来观察
Today I stayed again to watch

619
01:08:03,570 --> 01:08:06,240
我需要看看别人看到卡片后的反应
I need to see what happens when people read it

620
01:08:31,160 --> 01:08:32,230
来
Come

621
01:08:39,270 --> 01:08:41,910
我的疾病证明过期了
My sick certificate had expired

622
01:08:41,910 --> 01:08:43,840
所以我去看医生
That's why I went to see the doctor

623
01:08:43,840 --> 01:08:46,980
否则他们会送我去集中营 拜托了
They send me to a camp otherwise. Please!

624
01:08:46,980 --> 01:08:48,480
我发誓
I swear

625
01:08:48,480 --> 01:08:51,080
以我孩子们的生命发誓
by the lives of my children

626
01:08:51,080 --> 01:08:53,320
- 拜托了  - 两个儿子？
- Please  - Two sons?

627
01:08:53,320 --> 01:08:55,350
他们都是士兵吧
And they're both soldiers, right?

628
01:08:55,360 --> 01:08:57,090
两个都是
Both of them. Yes

629
01:08:58,190 --> 01:09:01,360
其中一个甚至是武装党卫队的
One of them is even in the Waffen-ss

630
01:09:01,360 --> 01:09:02,990
他们都还活着吧
And they're both alive, I hope?

631
01:09:03,000 --> 01:09:04,760
是的 这里
Yes. Here

632
01:09:06,070 --> 01:09:08,330
我的儿子卡尔 在波兰
Our Karl, in Poland

633
01:09:13,740 --> 01:09:17,680
这是好消息
Well... That's good news

634
01:09:17,680 --> 01:09:19,880
这人被当场抓住 有目击证人
So the man was caught red-handed. There are witnesses

635
01:09:19,880 --> 01:09:21,080
而这就是罪证
And here, the Corpus Delicti

636
01:09:21,080 --> 01:09:23,110
这显然是淘气鬼的字迹
It's obviously the writing of our hobgoblin

637
01:09:23,120 --> 01:09:25,020
拜托 埃舍里希 我们抓到他了
Come on, Escherich We've got him

638
01:09:25,020 --> 01:09:27,450
你也知道罪犯的特征 佐特
You know the criminal's profile as well as I do, Zott

639
01:09:27,450 --> 01:09:30,420
罪犯是个失去独子的机械工
We're looking for a mechanic who lost his only son

640
01:09:30,420 --> 01:09:32,820
你却拖来了这个可笑的家伙
And then you drag in this ridiculous character

641
01:09:32,830 --> 01:09:34,290
一个赌徒
a gambler

642
01:09:34,290 --> 01:09:36,830
而他甚至不住在我们的目标区域附近
who doesn't even live near our target area

643
01:09:36,830 --> 01:09:38,930
还有两个活着的儿子
with two children who are very much alive

644
01:09:40,130 --> 01:09:42,870
你的意思是 你相信我？
Does that, does that mean you believe me?

645
01:09:42,870 --> 01:09:44,470
- 是的 你可以走了  - 谢谢 谢谢
- Yes. You can go  - Thank you. Thank you

646
01:09:44,470 --> 01:09:45,470
- 出去吧  - 上帝保佑你
- Get out  - God bless you

647
01:09:45,470 --> 01:09:46,870
太谢谢你了
Thank you very much

648
01:09:52,310 --> 01:09:53,310
你真行
Bravo

649
01:09:56,520 --> 01:09:59,850
你做了什么 你放了那个陶器鬼？
You did what? You let your hobbygobby go?

650
01:09:59,850 --> 01:10:01,720
是淘气鬼 上校
Hobgoblin, Standartenfuhrer

651
01:10:01,720 --> 01:10:03,660
恕我直言
With due respect

652
01:10:03,660 --> 01:10:06,560
你虽然是我的上级 但身为党卫队的成员
you may be my superior, but as a member of the ss

653
01:10:06,560 --> 01:10:09,660
并不一定非要是刑事专家
you're not necessarily a criminalist

654
01:10:09,660 --> 01:10:13,100
我是个警察 我请求你不要干涉我的调查
I'm a policeman, and I'm asking you to let me do my job

655
01:10:13,100 --> 01:10:15,970
让我用我过去的经验
just as I have learned from my experience.

656
01:10:15,970 --> 01:10:17,270
经验？
Experience?

657
01:10:19,670 --> 01:10:21,440
你这样的人我见的多了
I know all about guys like you

658
01:10:21,440 --> 01:10:24,110
自作聪明的知识分子
Intellectuals, wise guys

659
01:10:24,110 --> 01:10:26,040
别弄脏我的地板
Don't mess up my floor!

660
01:10:26,050 --> 01:10:28,050
把你的血咽下去
Swallow your damn blood!

661
01:10:30,520 --> 01:10:33,620
起来 起来 来 起来
Up! Up, up, up, up, up! Come. Up

662
01:10:36,660 --> 01:10:38,160
你以为你聪明？
You think you're clever, huh?

663
01:10:38,160 --> 01:10:39,660
而我们都是党卫队的人
And we're just the guys from the ss

664
01:10:39,660 --> 01:10:41,490
什么都不懂对吗
who don't have a clue, right?

665
01:10:41,490 --> 01:10:44,760
说出来 我想听你说：我比你们聪明
Say it. I want to hear it I'm smarter than you guys

666
01:10:44,760 --> 01:10:46,700
说
Say it!

667
01:10:46,700 --> 01:10:49,670
- 说 我听不见  - 对不起
- Say it! I can't hear you  - I'm sorry

668
01:10:49,670 --> 01:10:50,840
什么
Huh?

669
01:10:53,340 --> 01:10:54,870
限你两天时间
You have two days.

670
01:10:56,380 --> 01:10:59,080
两天之内除掉那个你放走的人
Two days to eliminate the guy you let go

671
01:10:59,080 --> 01:11:01,210
现在把他赶出去
Now, get rid of that thing!

672
01:12:21,430 --> 01:12:22,860
昆格尔夫人？
Frau Quangel?

673
01:12:24,130 --> 01:12:26,130
你是汉斯的母亲吧
You're Hans's mother, right?

674
01:12:26,130 --> 01:12:28,730
- 是的  - 我是迪特里希
- Yes  - Uh, Dietrich

675
01:12:28,740 --> 01:12:30,640
我是汉斯的同学
I was one of Hans's classmates

676
01:12:30,640 --> 01:12:33,140
迪特里希 对
Dietrich. Of course

677
01:12:33,140 --> 01:12:34,610
你好吗
How are you?

678
01:12:34,610 --> 01:12:38,280
我很好 谢谢你 我还活着
Fine. Thank you Well, I'm alive

679
01:12:38,280 --> 01:12:40,280
很高兴你从战场回来了
I'm glad you've come back

680
01:12:42,410 --> 01:12:45,580
- 内克尔先生  - 对不起 我得走了
- Herr Necker?  - Excuse me, I have to go

681
01:12:49,320 --> 01:12:52,120
昆格尔夫人 我…
You know, Frau Quangel, I.

682
01:12:52,130 --> 01:12:53,720
我很怀念汉斯
I miss Hans a lot

683
01:13:19,990 --> 01:13:22,490
我和恩诺已经没什么关系了
I have nothing to do with Enno anymore

684
01:13:24,090 --> 01:13:27,560
他已经很久不是我丈夫了
He hasn't been my husband for a long time

685
01:13:27,560 --> 01:13:28,590
上帝作证
before god

686
01:13:36,440 --> 01:13:37,440
现在
Now.

687
01:13:38,970 --> 01:13:41,740
谈到哪儿了 对了
Where were we? Yes

688
01:13:41,740 --> 01:13:42,870
你正要告诉我
You were about to tell me

689
01:13:42,880 --> 01:13:44,980
去哪儿能找到你的前夫
how to find that ex-husband of yours

690
01:14:09,270 --> 01:14:10,900
你一直都藏在这里？
So here you've been hiding?

691
01:14:14,010 --> 01:14:15,910
我知道你跟卡片毫无关系 恩诺
I know you've nothing to do with the cards, Enno

692
01:14:15,910 --> 01:14:17,440
这是好消息 督查
Oh, that's good news, inspector...

693
01:14:17,440 --> 01:14:19,440
可党卫队的人认为就是你
but the guys from the ss think it was you

694
01:14:20,780 --> 01:14:22,850
现在他们说了算
And I'm afraid they're in charge now

695
01:14:25,750 --> 01:14:27,120
也管着我
In charge of me, too

696
01:14:29,050 --> 01:14:32,690
他们会逮捕你 会审讯你
They will arrest you, they will interrogate you

697
01:14:32,690 --> 01:14:33,930
以他们的方式
in their own way

698
01:14:37,560 --> 01:14:39,200
那我还不如死了
I'd rather be dead

699
01:14:42,000 --> 01:14:43,130
你说的对
You're right

700
01:14:44,600 --> 01:14:46,000
你还不如死了
You'd rather be dead

701
01:15:02,120 --> 01:15:05,090
- 呃  - 嘘
- Uh.  - Shh.

702
01:15:06,530 --> 01:15:09,860
没关系 这样更好一些
It's alright It's better this way

703
01:15:12,970 --> 01:15:15,300
- 不 求你  - 该死的
- No. Please. No!  - Shit!

704
01:15:30,250 --> 01:15:31,750
自杀？
Suicide?

705
01:15:33,190 --> 01:15:34,950
好消息 埃舍里希
Good news, Escherich

706
01:15:36,660 --> 01:15:38,320
绞索收紧了
The noose has tightened

707
01:15:39,990 --> 01:15:41,130
嗯？
Hm?

708
01:15:41,760 --> 01:15:43,190
没有新卡片了吧
No new cards?

709
01:15:43,760 --> 01:15:44,800
暂时还没有
Not yet

710
01:15:45,560 --> 01:15:46,730
没有了
No

711
01:15:48,300 --> 01:15:49,370
嗯
Hm

712
01:17:51,390 --> 01:17:53,420
谢谢你顶替弗里茨
Thanks for taking over for Fritz

713
01:18:03,570 --> 01:18:05,040
快到了
It's getting closer

714
01:18:32,560 --> 01:18:35,570
昆格尔工头机器过热了
Foreman Quangel, the machine is overheating

715
01:18:35,570 --> 01:18:37,100
关掉它
Turn it off!

716
01:19:58,180 --> 01:20:00,180
你怎么不干活
Don't you have anything to do?

717
01:20:13,800 --> 01:20:14,830
路德维格
Ludwig

718
01:20:17,370 --> 01:20:19,070
有东西给你
There's something for you

719
01:20:28,010 --> 01:20:29,910
这很严重
It's quite something

720
01:20:29,920 --> 01:20:31,580
最好交给管理层
Better take it to the management

721
01:20:32,550 --> 01:20:33,950
你是个党代表
You're a party representative

722
01:20:35,050 --> 01:20:38,520
你必须这么做按规矩办事
You have to do it Stick by the rules

723
01:20:58,580 --> 01:20:59,580
喂
Yes, sir

724
01:21:14,260 --> 01:21:16,130
今天上班的所有人
Everyone on today's shift

725
01:21:16,130 --> 01:21:18,230
- 姓名地址  - 好的
- Their names, addresses  - Of course

726
01:21:18,230 --> 01:21:20,560
此人肯定住在克利斯堡
Our man must live somewhere between christburger

727
01:21:20,570 --> 01:21:21,970
霍德维克斯特和加布隆斯基特之间的附近
chodowieckistr and jablonskistr

728
01:21:21,970 --> 01:21:24,570
没人住在那个地址 督查
No, nobody with that address, inspector

729
01:21:26,770 --> 01:21:28,740
工头是谁 谁对工人最了解
Who is the foreman? Who knows his men best?

730
01:21:28,740 --> 01:21:31,110
- 是弗里茨·肯帕  - 马上叫他来
- Well, that's Fritz Kemper  - Well, get him here at once

731
01:21:31,110 --> 01:21:33,840
这不可能他 今早伤到自己了
That's impossible He injured himself this morning

732
01:21:33,850 --> 01:21:35,810
- 谁顶替他的  - 是昆格尔
- And who replaced him?  - It's Quangel

733
01:21:35,820 --> 01:21:37,980
另一个班次的奥托·昆格尔
Otto Quangel from the other shift

734
01:21:37,980 --> 01:21:39,350
他的名字不在名单上
Well, his name is not in the list

735
01:21:39,350 --> 01:21:40,720
你不是说所有的人吗
I, I thought it was complete

736
01:21:40,720 --> 01:21:43,320
对不起 他今天只是来帮忙
Sorry. Uh, he's just helping out today

737
01:21:43,320 --> 01:21:45,120
当然 他不了解这些工人
Of course, he does not know the people

738
01:21:45,120 --> 01:21:47,190
他住在哪儿
Where does he live?

739
01:21:47,190 --> 01:21:48,490
奥托·昆格尔
Otto Quangel

740
01:22:05,640 --> 01:22:07,180
沃尔特 奥托在哪儿
Walter, where is Otto?

741
01:22:48,250 --> 01:22:50,150
早上好 昆格尔工头
Good morning, foreman Quangel

742
01:22:52,020 --> 01:22:53,160
早上好
Good morning

743
01:22:57,330 --> 01:22:59,360
请坐
Please, have a seat

744
01:23:18,320 --> 01:23:19,520
昆格尔夫人
Frau Quangel!

745
01:23:21,990 --> 01:23:24,120
我们知道你在家
We know you are here!

746
01:23:25,120 --> 01:23:26,990
开门
Open the door!

747
01:23:46,510 --> 01:23:47,950
看看这个 昆格尔
Look at this Quangel

748
01:23:49,280 --> 01:23:51,280
你肯定会对此感兴趣
This will surely interest you

749
01:23:52,920 --> 01:23:54,690
你觉得这是什么
What do you think that is?

750
01:24:03,290 --> 01:24:05,300
别装蒜了 昆格尔
Don't even make the effort, Quangel

751
01:24:07,970 --> 01:24:11,940
总共是两百六十七张卡片
There are exactly 267 cards

752
01:24:16,340 --> 01:24:18,410
你是在数有多少吗
Is that the number you were looking for?

753
01:24:19,340 --> 01:24:20,580
想想吧 昆格尔
Think about it, Quangel

754
01:24:21,880 --> 01:24:24,520
每张卡片都是别人上交的
Every single card was voluntarily turned into us

755
01:24:24,520 --> 01:24:25,720
主动上交
voluntarily

756
01:24:25,720 --> 01:24:28,520
我们自己没找到一张
We didn't find any ourselves

757
01:24:28,520 --> 01:24:29,990
他们都迫不及待的上交给我们
They couldn't wait to hand them over to us

758
01:24:29,990 --> 01:24:32,290
这些人都是
all those people

759
01:24:32,290 --> 01:24:35,390
有的人被捕了 有一个自杀了
Some were arrested, one committed suicide

760
01:24:37,860 --> 01:24:40,160
你凭什么相信
How could you seriously believe

761
01:24:40,170 --> 01:24:42,000
你能改变什么
that you would change anything

762
01:24:42,000 --> 01:24:44,740
昆格尔工头
you, foreman Quangel?

763
01:24:46,270 --> 01:24:47,970
- 谁自杀了  - 这不重要
- Who killed himself?  - It doesn't matter

764
01:24:47,970 --> 01:24:50,510
一个小人物无关紧要
A small fish. Insignificant

765
01:24:50,510 --> 01:24:52,510
每个人都重要
Everyone is significant

766
01:24:54,210 --> 01:24:56,850
- 这是我的错  - 这就对了
- It's my fault  - Oh, there we go

767
01:24:58,180 --> 01:25:00,180
现在你认罪了
Now you have admitted your crime

768
01:25:01,520 --> 01:25:03,820
你准确的告诉我 昆格尔
Tell me, Quangel, precisely

769
01:25:03,820 --> 01:25:06,390
你写了多少卡片
How many cards did you write yourself

770
01:25:06,390 --> 01:25:07,760
总共多少
I mean, altogether?

771
01:25:09,460 --> 01:25:11,460
两百八十五张
Two hundred and eighty five

772
01:25:13,570 --> 01:25:15,070
十八张
Eighteen

773
01:25:17,940 --> 01:25:20,000
只有十八张卡片没被上交
Eighteen cards weren't turned in

774
01:25:24,110 --> 01:25:26,110
另外我们抓到了安娜
By the way, we have Anna

775
01:25:28,710 --> 01:25:31,720
那就放了她 这跟她没关系
Then let her go She has nothing to do with it

776
01:25:31,720 --> 01:25:33,580
我知道你在撒谎 昆格尔
I know you are lying, Quangel

777
01:25:33,590 --> 01:25:35,090
卡片内容是你老婆口述的
Your wife dictated what to write

778
01:25:35,090 --> 01:25:36,950
看我像是那种
Do I look like someone who would let his wife

779
01:25:36,960 --> 01:25:38,960
听老婆口述的人吗
dictate things to him?

780
01:25:40,230 --> 01:25:42,360
一直都是我的主意
It was my idea from the beginning

781
01:25:42,360 --> 01:25:45,800
都是我设计的 我自己携带出去
I thought it all up I carried it out by myself

782
01:25:46,560 --> 01:25:48,100
她认罪了
She confessed

783
01:25:48,100 --> 01:25:49,230
这是你撒谎了
Now you're lying

784
01:25:50,640 --> 01:25:53,670
她认罪了 她不希望你独占功劳
She confessed. She didn't want you to get all the credit

785
01:25:59,640 --> 01:26:01,650
我会签字认罪
I'll sign my confession

786
01:26:02,810 --> 01:26:05,820
不过 督查 安娜
but, inspector, Anna

787
01:26:06,620 --> 01:26:08,720
请不要牵连
please, don't

788
01:26:12,220 --> 01:26:16,190
没这个必要
It's, it's not necessary

789
01:26:28,440 --> 01:26:30,440
派个记录员到我办公室来
Send a recording clerk to my office

790
01:26:49,690 --> 01:26:51,700
- 打扰一下长官  - 怎么了
- Excuse me, sir  - Yes

791
01:27:02,840 --> 01:27:05,580
啊 埃舍里希
Ah, Escherich

792
01:27:21,060 --> 01:27:22,690
为淘气鬼干杯
To the hobgoblin!

793
01:27:59,970 --> 01:28:00,970
昆格尔
Quangel

794
01:29:16,940 --> 01:29:19,710
- 安娜  - 奥托
- Anna  - Otto

795
01:29:39,500 --> 01:29:42,230
- 你知道会发生什么吧  - 是的
- You know what will happen?  - Yes

796
01:29:44,070 --> 01:29:46,500
是改变不了的
It can't be changed

797
01:29:46,510 --> 01:29:48,940
我知道 奥托
I know, Otto

798
01:29:52,240 --> 01:29:53,780
这无所谓
It doesn't matter

799
01:29:56,850 --> 01:29:57,850
是的
No

800
01:30:15,870 --> 01:30:17,730
全体起立
All rise!

801
01:30:27,880 --> 01:30:29,910
- 希特勒万岁  - 希特勒万岁
- Heil Hitler  - Heil Hitler

802
01:30:49,430 --> 01:30:50,530
时间到
Time's up

803
01:31:01,810 --> 01:31:04,380
别怕 我的孩子
Don't be afraid, my child

804
01:31:05,980 --> 01:31:07,780
别怕
Don't be afraid

805
01:31:17,660 --> 01:31:21,570
弗洛姆法官 你能陪我一下吗
Judge Fromm, would you stay with me a moment?

806
01:31:21,570 --> 01:31:24,530
我会闭上眼睛假装是奥拓
I'll close my eyes and pretend it is Otto

807
01:32:01,910 --> 01:32:03,140
时间到 昆格尔
Time, Quangel

808
01:32:10,080 --> 01:32:11,510
穿上
Put these on

809
01:32:39,540 --> 01:32:40,980
我能为你做什么吗
Can I do something for you?

810
01:32:42,950 --> 01:32:45,150
你需要什么吗
Is there something you need?

811
01:32:45,150 --> 01:32:46,720
卡片和一支笔
The card and a pen

812
01:32:51,960 --> 01:32:53,460
你还是把她抓走了
You took her anyway

813
01:34:13,400 --> 01:34:15,710
我看过你所有的卡片淘气鬼
I read all your cards, hobgoblin

814
01:34:17,270 --> 01:34:19,610
你和你老婆的
Yours and your wife's

815
01:34:21,580 --> 01:34:25,150
我是唯一全部看过的人
I am the only person who read all of them.

816
01:34:27,080 --> 01:34:29,150
全部除了十八张
All of them, except for 18

817
01:34:32,490 --> 01:34:34,160
十八张卡片
Eighteen cards

